[From an advertisement in the Adventist Review]<br>
(a logo) "Honor God, and praise his greatness,<br>
        Worship the maker of Heaven and earth and sea and<br>
        the springs of water.  Rev 14:6,7"<br>
<p>
Seven plenary sessions, seventeen workshops, resurrection pageant.<br>
April 7-10, 1993, Riverside, California<br>
<p>
A spiritual growth opportunity for pastors, lay worship leaders, youth<br>
leaders, women in church leadership, those exploring a theology of<br>
worship and the arts, sponsored by the Southeastern California<br>
Conference of <br>
seventh-day Adventists, with the Pacific Union Conference, and the North<br>
American Division.<br>
<p>
For more information, write or call:  Audray Johnson, Worship Conference,<br>
11330 Pierce Street, Riverside, CA  92515<br>
<p>
Phone  (909) 359-5800  ext 296   Fax  (909)688-1797<br>
<p>
Speakers listed include J. David Newman, Monte Sahlin, Hyveth Williams,<br>
Robert Webber, Caleb Rosado, Lyell Heise.<br>
<p>
<p>
-----<br>
Is anyone going to this conference?<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
