<title>Feb_1993: Re: Can Satan read my mind? (Or yours?)</title>
<h1>Re: Can Satan read my mind? (Or yours?)</h1>
Lisa Parry (<i>parry@peter.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 15 Feb 1993 12:21:04 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#145">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#145">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#145">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#145">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0146.html">Lisa Parry: "Women in the church"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0144.html">MARK BILBY: "Re: Women's issues"</a>
