<title>Feb_1993: Can Satan Read Minds???</title>
<h1>Can Satan Read Minds???</h1>
Michael Merginio (<i>merginim@edmund.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 15 Feb 1993 11:34:24 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#147">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#147">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#147">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#147">[ author ]</a>
