<title>Feb_1993: Women and the church of LDS</title>
<h1>Women and the church of LDS</h1>
Ruben Gonzalez (<i>ruben@ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 16 Feb 93 16:21:42 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#159">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#159">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#159">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#159">[ author ]</a>
