Hi all,<br>
<p>
Cheryl, I would be interested in knowning the status of women in the <br>
church of LDS. Is it a current issue ? <br>
<p>
Of the latter-day prophets in the LDS church, how many are or have been women ?<br>
<p>
What of the 12 apostles in the LDS church how many of those are women ?<br>
<p>
What about the membership of the 2 quorums of 70 ?<br>
<p>
what percentage of the ministers are women ?<br>
<p>
What percentage of the elders :) are women ?<br>
<p>
Ruben.<br>
