Hi all,<br>
Even though I'm an "Active-PASSIVE" SDA Net, ( I am 98% reader almost all the t<br>
ime).<br>
I felt that I should give my "TWO BITS" of participation in this "HOT POTATOES"<br>
Women &amp; SDA/men's Church...<br>
And I guess, the best way to start it,is from the very beginning...<br>
First, let me clarify you all that my BIBLE is an old faschioned Portuguese<br>
Bible, ( I do NOT know if it came from KJV, NIV, Erasmus or whatsoever...) The<br>
only thing I can think of it is that: If to Santan was given the power to des<br>
troy all the BIBLES in the world (every versions) and from that remained just<br>
the Salms 23:1 (it would be enough) to assure the Salvation to all of us!<br>
Am I wrong? ... Ok, lets go to the issue; WOMENS and SDA Church..(men's church)<br>
I think (if someone show me I'm wrong I accept it) this very problem started<br>
very long long time ago, if not, lets take a trip with me to Eden's Garden:<br>
Is every one on board? Ok, good! Do you remember how did sin make its way to<br>
this world???? exactly... was right there... Gen 3 (all) describe it to us.<br>
(I'd like you all give a special attention to the verse 16... even though I onl<br>
y have read the intire Bible, twice in all my entire life, I think all this<br>
problem about women be or not be in charge of something have its roots right<br>
there. There were our first parents; Adam &amp; Eve and with them the SIN and with<br>
sin our decrect to death even before we were born... OK!<br>
<p>
4,000 thousands something years later... in Appostle's time, we find Paul<br>
Saying to the Conrinthos how should women be presented to the church....<br>
( I Corinthos 11). If that was not enough, in another accasion, the same<br>
Paul appears again, this time to the church of Ephesus telling to the<br>
.... Adventists of olds?!?! about the duties of the women... (Ephesus 5: 22-31)<br>
Well, if we as an Adventist, who have the "Holy Scriptures" as a rule of life,<br>
really believe in what is written on it, them we should use the Gamaliel's word<br>
(PHARISEE) as an example, and more... " We as a GOD's servants should do our<br>
part in the divulgation of the goospell, and let the results with GOD". Do you<br>
remember who said that? Yeah.. that's right, was her. BTW... Isn't she<br>
femminine? So why all this noise???<br>
<p>
Isn't the Bible the best guide (software) available to us?<br>
Isn't the SDA Church the best (Hardware developed) since 1844 to run this<br>
valuable "SOFTWARE"?<br>
SO, lets our "Eavenly Macrosoft developer" take care of the "Interfaces"<br>
&amp; lets make this 3rd msg routine running smootly to the END, with a nice<br>
OUTPUT.... Thousand &amp; Thousands of Gigapeople to Him who CREATES us!<br>
<p>
Ademir P. Soares         NASA - Goddard Institute for Space Studies - NY - USA<br>
