It is a question of why, rather than what. SDAs do tend to<br>
abstain from certain foods, but not in deference to the<br>
"food laws" as such. <br>
<p>
<i>&gt; It also means because our bodies are the temples</i><br>
                ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^<br>
<i>&gt;of the Holy Spirit, we are to care for them intelligently.</i><br>
