<i>&gt;most healthful diet possible and abstain from the unclean </i><br>
<i>&gt;foods identified in the Scriptures.  [...]</i><br>
<p>
ie, not "because it is part of God's law". SDAs are not in<br>
favour of rape either, and once again this is an attitude<br>
based on more than just the law, ceremonial, moral, or<br>
otherwise.<br>
