I have a problem with the word "binding".  We do NOT consider this "binding".<br>
They are laws that make common sense, but in no case are the mandatory for<br>
either church membership, OR salvation.  That is, you can't be disfellowshipped<br>
for not following the health laws in the old testament.<br>
<p>
