to write a 7 to 10 page paper on Romans 6:12-14.  The vs. 14 states that<br>
we are no longer under law [at all] but under grace.  I have been stuck on<br>
that more than any other part of the verses.  I'm not sure how to take<br>
that.  Reference to Ex. 20? or all of the OT laws  or what?  (at all was<br>
added for my emphases)<br>
