<title>Feb_1993: Re: Shootout in Texas</title>
<h1>Re: Shootout in Texas</h1>
Dennis M DeLeon (<i>dmd9@midway.uchicago.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sun, 28 Feb 93 16:26:53 CST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#252">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#252">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#252">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#252">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0251.html">a11111arne@attmail.com: "Re: Shootout in Texas"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0247.html">Steven Timm: "Shootout in Texas"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
I just heard the same report about a shootout between <br>
federal agents and a heavily armed "cult group" in Waco,<br>
Texas.  Apparently 4 agents and at least one group member<br>
were killed.  The group is the Branch Davidians, and the <br>
confrontation apparently started when agents tried to arrest<br>
the leader, Vernon Howell, for violation of gun control laws.  <br>
The report did identify this group as an offshoot of the SDA <br>
church.  Hopefully someone else knows more...<br>
<p>
Dennis<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
<p>
<ul>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0251.html">a11111arne@attmail.com: "Re: Shootout in Texas"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0247.html">Steven Timm: "Shootout in Texas"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
