<title>Nov_1992: Re: Earvin "Magic" Johnson</title>
<h1>Re: Earvin "Magic" Johnson</h1>
Bill Oblitey (<i>72450.2430@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>11 Nov 92 14:10:14 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#22">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#22">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#22">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#22">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
