<!-- body="start" -->
Steve, <br>
<p>
Any SDA pastor that would like to have the weekly fax from the GC/NAD<br>
faxed them should send their fax number to Monte Sahlin. His fax number is<br>
(301) 680-6464. This will be an experiment with a Pastors' Fax Hotline and<br>
will be conducted later this year. I am sure the pastors having access to<br>
a fax machine would be aware of this but this must be a strictly fax line<br>
without a person answering first. This is no problem of course if you are<br>
using one phone line because there are inexpensive devices that will<br>
sense the call and if it is a fax call will switch it appropriately even<br>
though the person is using only one phone line.<br>
<p>
.........Paul<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
