<title>Nov_1992: RE: Foot Washing, Husband/Wife</title>
<h1>RE: Foot Washing, Husband/Wife</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 11 Nov 92 20:53:31 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
