     Status codes<br>
	N = new (licensed within past year)<br>
	A = Active DXer<br>
	I = Inactive in hobby<br>
<p>
     Class codes<br>
	NOV = Novice<br>
	NCT = no code Technician<br>
	TCH = Technician with HF privileges<br>
	GEN = General<br>
	ADV = Advanced<br>
	EXT = Extra<br>
	<br>
