<title>Nov_1992: Re: hermeneutics</title>
<h1>Re: hermeneutics</h1>
McCluskey G (<i>glenm@usl.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 18 Nov 92 10:39:00 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#54">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#54">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#54">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#54">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0055.html">Raylene: "Hermeneutics &amp; theology for everyperson"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0053.html">cheryl berthelsen: "Ham radio operators on SDAnet"</a>
