<title>Nov_1992: Hermeneutics &amp; theology for everyperson</title>
<h1>Hermeneutics &amp; theology for everyperson</h1>
Raylene (<i>CHRMD@cc.newcastle.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>19 Nov 1992 13:44:14 +1100</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#55">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#55">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#55">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#55">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0056.html">patricio d navia: "Last Night's 48 hours (CBS) program."</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0054.html">McCluskey G: "Re: hermeneutics"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0060.html">Bill Oblitey: "Re: Hermeneutics &amp; theology for everyperson"</a>
