<title>Nov_1992: FW: baby boomer tolerance</title>
<h1>FW: baby boomer tolerance</h1>
ARKUSINSKI ANDY  (<i>/S=ARKUSINSKI_ANDY/O=MSMAIL/PRMD=SMITHS_IND./ADMD=TELEMAIL/C=US/@mailtalk.si.comARKUSINSKI ANDY </i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 24 Nov 92 18:46:07 GMT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#79">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#79">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#79">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#79">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0080.html">ARKUSINSKI ANDY : "More on Compuserve Forum"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0078.html">Steven Timm: "Re: baby boomer tolerance"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
