<title>Nov_1992: More on Compuserve Forum</title>
<h1>More on Compuserve Forum</h1>
ARKUSINSKI ANDY  (<i>72450.2430@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>24 Nov 92 14:38:54 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#80">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#80">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#80">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#80">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0081.html">Pam Harris: "Adventist Shamanism"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0079.html">ARKUSINSKI ANDY : "FW: baby boomer tolerance"</a>
