<title>May_1992: What does the SDA church about this?</title>
<h1>What does the SDA church about this?</h1>
Scott Mattes (<i>COTRSSM@sea04vm.navsea.navy.mil</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 07 May 92 11:31:03 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#7">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#7">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#7">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#7">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0008.html">Scott Mattes: "Did I miss something?"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0006.html">James Dunn: "Re: Free speech"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
