<h1>More news on the transition</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+%ANDREW.CMU.EDU%CMU.EDU@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 11 May 1992 23:14:04 -0400</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#12">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#12">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#12">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#12">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0013.html">Dave Buxton: "Is the SDA church Ecumenical?"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0011.html">David Plaisted: "absent from the body"</a>
