We have received circular type letters from his wife from time to time<br>
indicating that she is working to complete at least some of his<br>
projects that were researched in his trip around the world to gather<br>
stories and video footage of historic early hundreds AD Sabbath keeping.<br>
I have not received any notice that its available, but then its been<br>
a few months.  Seems like its time for an update.<br>
