<h1>Re: Let me see if I have this correct on saved by works</h1>
Paul Gates (<i>70516.420@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>17 May 92 22:18:41 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#43">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#43">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#43">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#43">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0044.html">Dave Buxton: "Re: Death Afterlife"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0042.html">Steven Timm: "The Second Annual SDAnet contest"</a>
