<!-- body="start" -->
Hi all,<br>
<p>
	Heres a question I would like to get your opinion about.<br>
<p>
Which do you think it would be more correct to say; when one is converted<br>
one is saved (full stop) OR one is on the path of salvation ?<br>
<p>
There is a very important yet subtle distinction here.<br>
<p>
Ruben.<br>
