<title>May_1992: Re: tithe and committment</title>
<h1>Re: tithe and committment</h1>
McCluskey G (<i>glenm@usl.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 19 May 92 13:57:37 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#56">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#56">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#56">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#56">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0057.html">Bob Moynihan: "re: Commitment and Finances"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0055.html">Dave Buxton: "Re: Commitment and Finances"</a>
