<title>May_1992: The Reformation and The Comfortable Pew (follow-up)</title>
<h1>The Reformation and The Comfortable Pew (follow-up)</h1>
Fred Christiansen (<i>fredch@mcd.mot.com</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 22 May 92 10:40:56 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#72">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#72">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#72">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#72">[ author ]</a>
