<title>May_1992: Re: tithe and committment</title>
<h1>Re: tithe and committment</h1>
Scott Mattes (<i>COTRSSM@sea04vm.navsea.navy.mil</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 27 May 92 11:32:56 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#84">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#84">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#84">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#84">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0085.html">Lola: "tithing and church office"</a>
