<h1>Tithing</h1>
Stan Macasieb (<i>Stan_Macasieb@isu.comm.mot.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 27 May 1992 15:08:45 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#88">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#88">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#88">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#88">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0089.html">Rhonda Gaines: "Re: Sabbath or sabbaths?"</a>
