Tony Dyson wrote:<br>
<p>
<i>&gt;I'm sure there is room for both on SDAnet, providing</i><br>
<i>&gt;there is more of "my opinion is only my opinion", and less of "your</i><br>
<i>&gt;opinion is only your opinion"!</i><br>
