Very true.  It is difficult to focus on the "my opinion is only my <br>
opinion" side<br>
when reverting to "my opinion is God's opinion, and all else is naught."<br>
<p>
Howerve, let's not faulter at that which is diffcult, but with Christ, <br>
move above<br>
and beyond it.<br>
