<title>Jun_1993: Re: net.athiests</title>
<h1>Re: net.athiests</h1>
Tony Dyson (<i>PHTH1@cc.newcastle.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>01 Jun 1993 12:26:30 +1000</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#2">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#2">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#2">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#2">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0003.html">Dan Drazen: "Re: Notes on the day of Pentecost"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0001.html">Tony Dyson: "Basis for discussion"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0023.html">Dan Blake: "Re: net.athiests"</a>
