<title>Jun_1993: Re: Notes on the day of Pentecost</title>
<h1>Re: Notes on the day of Pentecost</h1>
Ruben Gonzalez (<i>ruben@ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 1 Jun 93 15:07:01 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#5">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#5">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#5">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#5">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0006.html">Steven Timm: "Re: Notes on the day of Pentecost"</a>
