For those who might be interested.<br>
<p>
The SDA gay youth who's family disowned him, has been placed<br>
with a supportive family, by "non" - Christian professionals.<br>
<p>
Upon visiting the center, I recognized pamphlets and brochures<br>
from various religious groups and denominations which offer non<br>
judgmental spiritual support.  I'd like to get some SDA inforamtion in the<br>
youth center, just in case more of our young people find themselves<br>
there.  If anyone has knowledge of information, please let me know.<br>
<p>
Marcus<br>
