Plays work quite well at summer camp, academy and college services,<br>
and even in the my local church here in Seattle.<br>
<p>
Just because Jesus reaps where He has not sown, or gathers where He hasn't<br>
scattered, is no cause for us to sit on the talents the He has given <br>
us.  I believe<br>
we are to not only go into all the world, but to fulfill the world of <br>
communicative<br>
possibilities Christ, through science and education have informed us about.<br>
<p>
Has God given us knowledge of learning styles, and temperaments so that we<br>
ignore them for the sake of "traditional" approaches (vis-a-vis)?  <br>
Let's get wisdom,<br>
knowledge &amp; understanding... and make it practical in reaching people - <br>
ALL people.<br>
<p>
Marcus<br>
