<h1>Re:  Historically Correct Meets Politically Correct</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Thu,  3 Jun 93 13:27:46 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#30">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#30">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#30">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#30">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0031.html">Marcus Stringer: "Revisit"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0029.html">David Plaisted: "acceptance in the Lord"</a>
