<h1>RE: Sex changes</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Fri,  4 Jun 93 11:03:54 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#53">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#53">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#53">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#53">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0054.html">Harvey Brenneise: "Re: Gun, Guns"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0052.html">Fred Christiansen: "Re: net.athiests"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
