I'm shocked that you would even ask whether or not to invite such a <br>
person to church. God doesn't look at what sex we are, or what body <br>
parts we currently have. God looks at the heart and character of the <br>
individual. Our character is a reflection of God not our sex. Persons <br>
who have undergone sex changes are as much a child of God as anyone <br>
else. God Grace is sufficient for everyone and anyone.<br>
