Has anyone read the introduction to The Great Controversy?  Has anyone<br>
read 1Selected Messages?  Has anyone read Acts, and the accounts which<br>
occurred in the young Christian church re: doctrine, Jews/Gentiles, and the<br>
Jerusalem Counsel or Convention?<br>
<p>
What, or rather, WHO is our focus?  Putting our focus where it should be,<br>
upon Jesus Christ, does not nullify doing good works.  To the contrary!<br>
Christ will work His works, and live his life through us.<br>
<p>
I know I've mentioned it before, but various tones in net discussions make me<br>
want to mention it again.  Alden Thompson, a religion professor at Walla Walla<br>
college has written a great book, (excellent = I agree w/ everything) <br>
book called<br>
"Inspiration".  I invite you and all net folk to read it if you <br>
haven't, or if you already<br>
have, *prayerfully* re-read it.<br>
<p>
Marcus<br>
