Steve,<br>
	I grew up without television.  It was not until I was in college that<br>
I watched televison for more than 1 or 2 hours a YEAR. Literally. then I<br>
watched a *LOT* of Startrek, Moonbase Alpha, and other science fiction.<br>
I turned my Tv off 7 years ago, (except for occasional news, such as<br>
elections, the riots in LA, and the Waco thing).  We don't watch anything<br>
with violenc in it.<br>
