Well, before picking on the left, I would advise you to have a look at the<br>
publication "Church and State" which is published by the American's United<br>
for Separation of Church and State. The board of directors boasts MANY<br>
SDA and Baptist clergy. It identifies the real enemy of church and state<br>
separtation as the Relgious Right.<br>
<p>
