[The SDA establishment has done nothing but pick on the religious right<br>
for the last 16 years.  This, however, represents quite a shift from the <br>
early 1960's, when the gloom 'n doomers were predicting that John F. Kennedy,<br>
a Catholic, would sell the country over to the Pope.  The plots of the <br>
religious right are regularly discussed on SDAnet.  I thought perhaps <br>
it was time to look at the left (and I speak as a Democrat).  SCT]<br>
