Added comment.  1 Cor 5 does support judging those inside the church,<br>
and expelling "the wicked man from among you."  In chapter 4, Paul speaks<br>
against judging.  Some background information is needed, the thought<br>
can't change so drastically without a reason.  What is Paul talking about?<br>
I personally am confused and will have to read and pray about it.<br>
<p>
Marcus<br>
