<i>&gt;So we should not assume that the spirit of the law is any more lenient</i><br>
<i>&gt;than the letter of the law.</i><br>
<p>
Precisely.  Yea, it calls us to an even higher level of commitment to<br>
Christ and His principles being lived out in our lives.<br>
<p>
Love God with everything you've got, and your neighbor as yourself.<br>
We must first know God (not just ABOUT God) in order to truly love God.<br>
Loving God will overflow into loving humans.  Can't love God while we<br>
are unloving to humans.<br>
<p>
Marcus<br>
