<title>Jun_1993: Re: &gt; Re: Gun, Guns</title>
<h1>Re: &gt; Re: Gun, Guns</h1>
Steve Hix (<i>fiddler@dobbs.eng.sun.com</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 10 Jun 93 12:25:17 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#130">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#130">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#130">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#130">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0131.html">Dan Drazen: "Re: Seventh-day Wimps"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0129.html">Steven Timm: "Re: Seventh-day Wimps"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0070.html">Ralf Simonsson: "&gt; Re: Gun, Guns"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
