<title>Jun_1993: Church discipline</title>
<h1>Church discipline</h1>
Ralf Simonsson (<i>/G=Ralf/S=Simonsson/O=Fimnet/@elisa.fi</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 11 Jun 1993 07:53:46 +0300</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#152">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#152">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#152">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#152">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
