<!-- body="start" -->
Re: Church discipline.<br>
<p>
I think church discipline is there toprotect the church not to judge<br>
people. I evil is creeping into the congregation, that is making harm to <br>
the church, then we have to get rid of the evil. One way is chirch discipline<br>
Church discipline i snot there to *punish* "naughy children", who might<br>
have problems with themselves and the world around. For them the church<br>
is there to help and cure through love and patience. But sometimes Satan is using <br>
people to create conflicts and disturbance (my poor english!) in the<br>
congregation. Then we have to swiftly get rid of the evil.<br>
<p>
Ralf<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
