<title>Jun_1993: Re: Biases and homosexuality</title>
<h1>Re: Biases and homosexuality</h1>
Raylene Dyson (<i>CHRMD@cc.newcastle.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>13 Jun 1993 16:28:29 +1000</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#173">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#173">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#173">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#173">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0174.html">Steve Hix: "Re: Shooting at Big Brother"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0172.html">(no name): "RE: SS ideas"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0148.html">Harvey Brenneise: "Biases and homosexuality"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0196.html">Woody Baker: "Re: Biases and homosexuality"</a>
