<title>Jun_1993: Re: Biases and homosexuality</title>
<h1>Re: Biases and homosexuality</h1>
Woody Baker (<i>woody@knapper.cactus.org</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 15 Jun 1993 08:59:15 CDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#196">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#196">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#196">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#196">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0197.html">Dan Crowe: "Dating outside the faith"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0195.html">Marcus Stringer: "FW: Colorado Methodists vow to fight Amendment 2"</a>
