I am a Ph.D. Student at Claremont Graduate School in California.<br>
<p>
I need to pilot test a survey that I am planning on using for my dissertation.<br>
<p>
 Can you help?<br>
<p>
I need a few people to agree to distribute this survey to 3-5 faculty at the<br>
college or university with which you  are affliated.  I will mail them to you<br>
with stamped addressed envelopes for each survey.  All I would ask you to do<br>
is hand the survey to five different people.<br>
<p>
Please write back via E-mail.<br>
<p>
